OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FThe mother of a Dorset girl whose life
OL,7,Fwas saved by local firefighters says
OL,8,Fthey must be protected from potential
OL,9,Ffunding cuts in the future.
OL,11,FLila-Claire Lambert was six years old
OL,12,Fwhen she was involved in a serious car
OL,13,Fcrash on the A37. Firefighters from
OL,14,FMaiden Newton attended and carried out
OL,15,Froadside CPR to save her.
OL,17,FNow, as the threat of closure
OL,18,Fcontinues to hang over eight fire
OL,19,Fstations in Dorset and Wiltshire, the
OL,20,FLambert family have shared Lila-
OL,21,FClaire's story in a bid to save them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
