PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FCarla Lambert, Lila-Claire's mother,
OL,7,Fsaid: "It was dire, she wasn't
OL,8,Fbreathing and had barely any pulse. I
OL,9,Fwas absolutely hysterical. Her brain
OL,10,Fwas swelling in her skull.
OL,12,F"The emergency care from those
OL,13,Ffirefighters saved her life. If it had
OL,14,Fbeen another five minutes she wouldn't
OL,15,Fhave made it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
