OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Dorset and
OL,7,FWiltshire Fire Authority proposed
OL,8,Fclosing stations at Bradford on Avon,
OL,9,FCharmouth, Cranborne, Hamworthy,
OL,10,FMaiden Newton, Mere, Ramsbury and
OL,11,FWilton.
OL,13,FIt said it was necessary to address a
OL,14,Ffunding gap of more than #1.2million.
OL,16,FFollowing local opposition, protests
OL,17,Fand a public consultation, the at-risk
OL,18,Fstations were given a reprieve.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FUnder a new plan by the fire
OL,7,Fauthority, Hamworthy Fire Station
OL,8,Fwould merge with Poole Fire Station
OL,9,Fand Wilton Fire Station would merge
OL,10,Fwith Salisbury Fire Station, both for
OL,11,Fa 12-month trial period.
OL,13,FThe six remaining stations included
OL,14,Fwithin the consultation proposals will
OL,15,Fremain operational and become part of
OL,16,Fa wider Service Modernisation
OL,17,FProgramme.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FHowever, the fire authority said that
OL,7,Fif it wasn't allowed to raise more
OL,8,Fmoney through council tax, then the
OL,9,Fclosures would go ahead.
OL,11,FAndy Elliott from the Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService Association explained: "Maiden
OL,13,FNewton and the other stations that are
OL,14,Fproposed to remain open, that is for a
OL,15,F12-month trial period and it's subject
OL,16,Fto government funding. And if that
OL,17,Ffunding doesn't come forward it's
OL,18,Flikely the stations will close."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
