OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FMs Lambert said: "I hope if a crash
OL,7,Flike that happened again that they
OL,8,Fwould be there so they get the best
OL,9,Fchance like Lila-Claire.
OL,11,F"She was airlifted to Southampton
OL,12,FHospital where the prognosis was
OL,13,Fterrible. She was in the PICU for 2
OL,14,Fweeks then she went to a Neuro ward.
OL,16,F"I was told she'd never walk, never
OL,17,Ftalk. I even had the organ donation
OL,18,Fpeople come to speak to me. But by
OL,19,Fsome miracle here she is."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FIn relation to the previously proposed
OL,7,Fclosure of Maiden Newton fire station,
OL,8,Fshe said she thought it was
OL,9,F"diabolical".
OL,11,F"It's just cuts on the wrong things
OL,12,Fall the time. I don't know how they
OL,13,Fcould even have considered it. How can
OL,14,Fyou put a price on people's lives?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
