OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,FDorset and Wiltshire's chief fire
OL,7,Fofficer Andy Cole said: "The Members
OL,8,FWorking Group met (on 4th June) to
OL,9,Fconsider the feedback received through
OL,10,Fthe public consultation on the
OL,11,Fpotential fire station closure
OL,12,Fproposals.
OL,14,F"They also received an update on the
OL,15,FService's financial position. I have
OL,16,Fhad some positive discussions with
OL,17,FGovernment and we are hopeful we will
OL,18,Fget some future council tax
OL,19,Fflexibility for ongoing funding
OL,20,Fstability.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@SpmpD@_pn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,F"I appreciate all the efforts from
OL,7,Feveryone who participated in the
OL,8,Fpublic consultation and particularly
OL,9,Fin raising matters about funding. The
OL,10,Flevel of engagement has been
OL,11,Fsignificant and has helped inform both
OL,12,FMembers and officers.
OL,14,F"As I have always said, if our
OL,15,Ffinancial position changes, my
OL,16,Fprofessional advice to the Fire and
OL,17,FRescue Authority would change.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,F"I am now in a position to change that
OL,7,Fadvice. While no decisions will be
OL,8,Fmade until 30th June, the Members
OL,9,FWorking Group have agreed to recommend
OL,10,Fthe below, subject to the Authority
OL,11,Fgetting future council tax flexibility
OL,12,Fin line with the national average for
OL,13,Ffire and rescue services from 2027/28:
OL,15,F"This recommendation seeks to avoid
OL,16,Fcompulsory redundancies and retain
OL,17,Ffrontline operational resources.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1781869673
OL,3,CMum recalls night firefighters from at-
OL,4,Crisk station saved her daughter's life
OL,6,F"Since I took the role of Chief Fire
OL,7,FOfficer I have been keen to modernise
OL,8,Fand create a fire and rescue service
OL,9,Ffit for the second half of the 21st
OL,10,Fcentury, because we must continue to
OL,11,Fadapt if we are to remain financially
OL,12,Fsustainable and operationally
OL,13,Feffective.
OL,15,F"The Government has also been clear
OL,16,Fthat additional financial flexibility
OL,17,Fmust be accompanied by a credible
OL,18,Fprogramme of modernisation. The final
OL,19,Frecommendations and papers for the
OL,20,FFire & Rescue Authority meeting will
OL,21,Fbe published on 22nd June."
OL,26,@}D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
